Q:- Find out the mail servers of the following domain : Ibm.com & Wipro.com

Ans:- IBM:- ibm.com
            Server:  UnKnown
            Address:  192.168.1.1

            Non-authoritative answer:
            ibm.com MX preference = 5, mail exchanger = mx0b-001b2d01.pphosted.com
            ibm.com MX preference = 5, mail exchanger = mx0a-001b2d01.pphosted.com
            
 So,IBM mail server is mail exchanger = mx0b-001b2d01.pphosted.com and mx0a-001b2d01.pphosted.com
 
 Wipro.com :- wipro.com
              Server:  UnKnown
              Address:  192.168.1.1

              Non-authoritative answer:
              wipro.com       MX preference = 0, mail exchanger = wipro-com.mail.protection.outlook.com

              wipro.com       nameserver = ns4.webindia.com
              wipro.com       nameserver = ns2.webindia.com
              wipro.com       nameserver = ns1.webindia.com
              
So,Wipro server is mail exchanger =ns4.webindia.com , nameserver = ns2.webindia.com &  nameserver = ns1.webindia.com


